  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p><span>Available for winter 2021/22, Chalet des Cascades is in the ultimate place to stay in Arc 2000, built into the piste with fantastic views and ski in/ski out access. </span><span>The open plan lounge and dining area has a central fireplace  and there’s a floating chill out area above with comfy sofas, giving another space to enjoy. There’s also a terrace area from the lounge giving panoramic views. and t</span><span>he indoor pool and sauna area is perfect to relax in after a full day of skiing. </span></p>]]></listingDescription>
