  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p><span><strong>Perfect location on a gentle piste</strong> so all levels of skier can ski to the door. The village of Arc 2000 is just 150 metres away and you walk uphill across the piste so bring suitable footwear. In the mornings just s</span><span>ki down to the Saint Jacques chairlift to discover Les Arcs and the full Paradiski area</span></p>
<p>As the chalet is in the middle of the piste then our staff will help you with the luggage. There is a skidoo with a trailer to transport luggage but this can be used only at certain times of the day, otherwise our staff can transport your luggage by sleigh. </p>
<p>Our partner ski hire shop is conveniently located at the Hotel Taj-I-Mah, just a couple of minutes' walk away (200m).</p>]]></locationDescription>
